message.body: Sooo nice! There was beer literally everywhere on the floor from the kitchen to the wall of bottles, but you probs got it already
I haven't cleaned the floor, I'm getting supplies for that. Probably tomorrow
You're too good for that house. I heard my roommates saw you by beyond bread today!
Yup, I was checking walgreens for cleaning supplies haha I'd already gotten paper towels at Albertson's
I washed the uss enterprise sheets and my own since I think someone slept in my bed
Haha really? It wasn't me for once. Probably of those high schoolers you guys hang out with
Maaaax, is anyone at your house right now?
Yes, the whole crew is here
Oh damn! Okay don't laugh at me but...can I stop by to pick up my flax seed?
Haha if you want. We'll just be watching Ralf fail at games
I need it!! Okay, I'll be there soon
